{"id":39,"parent_id":31,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":39,"title":"Mark 8","subtitle":"","short_title":"Mark","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 8"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus feeds the four thousand—He counsels, Beware of the leaven of the Pharisees—He heals a blind man in Bethsaida—Peter testifies that Jesus is the Christ."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.1","order":"03.04.008.4723"},["b","1"],"In those days the multitude being very great, and having nothing to eat, Jesus called his disciples",["i","unto him,"],"and saith unto them,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.2","order":"03.04.008.4724"},["b","2"],"I have compassion on the multitude, because they have now been with me three days, and have nothing to eat:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.3","order":"03.04.008.4725"},["b","3"],"And if I send them away fasting to their own houses, they will faint by the way: for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"divers"],"of them came from far."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.4","order":"03.04.008.4726"},["b","4"],"And his disciples answered him, From whence can a man satisfy these",["i","men"],"with bread here in the wilderness?"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.5","order":"03.04.008.4727"},["b","5"],"And he asked them, How many loaves have ye? And they said, Seven."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.6","order":"03.04.008.4728"},["b","6"],"And he commanded the people to sit down on the ground: and he took the seven loaves, and gave thanks, and brake, and gave to his disciples to set before",["i","them;"],"and they did set",["i","them"],"before the people."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.7","order":"03.04.008.4729"},["b","7"],"And they had a few small fishes: and he blessed, and commanded to set them also before",["i","them."]],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.8","order":"03.04.008.4730"},["b","8"],"So they did eat, and were filled: and they took up of the broken",["i","meat"],"that was left seven baskets."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.9","order":"03.04.008.4731"},["b","9"],"And they that had eaten were about four thousand: and he sent them away."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.10","order":"03.04.008.4732"},["b","10"],"¶And straightway he entered into a ship with his disciples, and came into the parts of Dalmanutha."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.11","order":"03.04.008.4733"},["b","11"],"And the Pharisees came forth, and began to question with him, seeking of him a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"sign"],"from heaven, tempting him."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.12","order":"03.04.008.4734"},["b","12"],"And he sighed deeply in his spirit, and saith, Why doth this generation seek after a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"sign"],"? verily I say unto you, There shall no sign be given unto this generation."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.13","order":"03.04.008.4735"},["b","13"],"And he left them, and entering into the ship again departed to the other side."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.14","order":"03.04.008.4736"},["b","14"],"¶Now",["i","the disciples"],"had forgotten to take bread, neither had they in the ship with them more than one loaf."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.15","order":"03.04.008.4737"},["b","15"],"And he charged them, saying, Take heed, beware of the leaven of the Pharisees, and",["i","of"],"the leaven of Herod."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.16","order":"03.04.008.4738"},["b","16"],"And they reasoned among themselves, saying,",["i","It is"],"because we have no bread."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.17","order":"03.04.008.4739"},["b","17"],"And when Jesus knew",["i","it,"],"he saith unto them, Why reason ye, because ye have no bread? perceive ye not yet, neither understand?",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"have"],"ye your heart yet",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"hardened"],"?"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.18","order":"03.04.008.4740"},["b","18"],"Having eyes, see ye not? and having ears, hear ye not? and do ye not remember?"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.19","order":"03.04.008.4741"},["b","19"],"When I brake the five loaves among five thousand, how many baskets full of fragments took ye up? They say unto him, Twelve."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.20","order":"03.04.008.4742"},["b","20"],"And when the seven among four thousand, how many baskets full of fragments took ye up? And they said, Seven."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.21","order":"03.04.008.4743"},["b","21"],"And he said unto them, How is it that ye do not understand?"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.22","order":"03.04.008.4744"},["b","22"],"¶And he cometh to Bethsaida; and they bring a blind man unto him, and besought him to touch him."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.23","order":"03.04.008.4745"},["b","23"],"And he took the blind man by the hand, and led him out of the town; and when he had spit on his eyes, and put his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"hands"],"upon him, he asked him if he saw",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"ought"],"."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.24","order":"03.04.008.4746"},["b","24"],"And he looked up, and said, I see men as trees, walking."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.25","order":"03.04.008.4747"},["b","25"],"After that he put",["i","his"],"hands again upon his eyes, and made him look up: and he was restored, and saw",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"every man"],"clearly."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.26","order":"03.04.008.4748"},["b","26"],"And he sent him away to his house, saying, Neither go into the town, nor tell",["i","it"],"to any in the town."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.27","order":"03.04.008.4749"},["b","27"],"¶And Jesus went out, and his disciples, into the towns of Cæsarea Philippi: and by the way he asked his disciples, saying unto them, Whom do men say that I am?"],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.28","order":"03.04.008.4750"},["b","28"],"And they answered, John the Baptist: but some",["i","say,"],"Elias; and others, One of the prophets."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.29","order":"03.04.008.4751"},["b","29"],"And he saith unto them, But whom say ye that I am? And Peter answereth and saith unto him, Thou art the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"Christ"],"."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.30","order":"03.04.008.4752"},["b","30"],"And he charged them that they should",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"tell"],"no man of him."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.31","order":"03.04.008.4753"},["b","31"],"And he began to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"teach"],"them, that the Son of man must suffer many things, and be rejected of the elders, and",["i","of"],"the chief priests, and scribes, and be killed, and after three days rise again."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.32","order":"03.04.008.4754"},["b","32"],"And he spake that saying openly. And Peter took him, and began to rebuke him."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.33","order":"03.04.008.4755"},["b","33"],"But when he had turned about and looked on his disciples, he rebuked Peter, saying, Get thee behind me,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"Satan"],": for",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_33b"},"thou savourest not"],"the things that be of God, but the things that be of men."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.34","order":"03.04.008.4756"},["b","34"],"¶And when he had called the people",["i","unto him"],"with his disciples also, he said unto them, Whosoever will come after me, let him",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"deny"],"himself, and take up his cross, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_34b"},"follow"],"me."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.35","order":"03.04.008.4757"},["b","35"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_35a"},"For"],"whosoever will save his life shall lose it; but whosoever shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_35b"},"lose"],"his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_35c"},"life"],"for my sake and the gospel’s, the same shall save it."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.36","order":"03.04.008.4758"},["b","36"],"For what shall it profit a man, if he shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_36a"},"gain"],"the whole world, and lose his own soul?"],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.37","order":"03.04.008.4759"},["b","37"],"Or what shall a man give in exchange for his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_37a"},"soul"],"?"],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.38","order":"03.04.008.4760"},["b","38"],"Whosoever therefore shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_38a"},"ashamed"],"of me and of my words in this adulterous and sinful generation; of him also shall the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_38b"},"Son of man"],"be ashamed, when he cometh in the glory of his Father with the holy",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_38c"},"angels"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.3a","order":"03.04.008.4761"},["b","3a"],["span.small","GR"],"some."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.11a","order":"03.04.008.4763"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.9"},"D&C 46:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/63.7.7-11"},"63:7 (7–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.12a","order":"03.04.008.4765"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/16.4.1-12"},"Matt. 16:4 (1–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.17a","order":"03.04.008.4767"},["b","17a"],["span.small","GR"],"do you still have hardened hearts?"],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.17b","order":"03.04.008.4769"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hardheartedness"},"TG Hardheartedness"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.23a","order":"03.04.008.4771"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/administrations-to-the-sick"},"TG Administrations to the Sick"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hands-laying-on-of"},"Hands, Laying on of"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.23b","order":"03.04.008.4773"},["b","23b"],["span.small","OR"],"anything."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.25a","order":"03.04.008.4775"},["b","25a"],["span.small","OR"],"everything."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.29a","order":"03.04.008.4777"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-messiah"},"TG Jesus Christ, Messiah"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.30a","order":"03.04.008.4779"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/9.21"},"Luke 9:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.31a","order":"03.04.008.4781"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-teaching-mode-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Teaching Mode of"],"."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.33a","order":"03.04.008.4783"},["b","33a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/12.5.5-6,34"},"Alma 12:5 (5–6, 34)"],"."],["div",{"id":"33b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.33b","order":"03.04.008.4785"},["b","33b"],["span.small","GR"],"you do not consider, cherish."],["div",{"id":"34a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.34a","order":"03.04.008.4787"},["b","34a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/self-mastery"},"TG Self-Mastery"],"."],["div",{"id":"34b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.34b","order":"03.04.008.4789"},["b","34b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-exemplar"},"TG Jesus Christ, Exemplar"],"."],["div",{"id":"35a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.35a","order":"03.04.008.4791"},["b","35a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-mark/8.37-38"},["span.small","JST"],"Mark 8:37–38 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"35b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.35b","order":"03.04.008.4793"},["b","35b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/9.24"},"Luke 9:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-luke/9.24-25"},["span.small","JST"],"Luke 9:24–25 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"35c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.35c","order":"03.04.008.4795"},["b","35c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/11.35"},"Heb. 11:35"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/11.35b"},["span.small","JST"],"Heb. 11:35 (Heb. 11:35 note",["i","b"],")"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/103.28.27-28"},"D&C 103:28 (27–28)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/martyrdom"},"TG Martyrdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"36a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.36a","order":"03.04.008.4797"},["b","36a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/45.5"},"Jer. 45:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"37a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.37a","order":"03.04.008.4799"},["b","37a"],["span.small","JST"],"Mark 8:39–40 … soul?",["i","Therefore deny yourselves of these, and be not ashamed of me."]],["div",{"id":"38a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.38a","order":"03.04.008.4801"},["b","38a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/8.28.24-28"},"1 Ne. 8:28 (24–28)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/shame"},"TG Shame"],"."],["div",{"id":"38b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.38b","order":"03.04.008.4803"},["b","38b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-son-of-man"},"TG Jesus Christ, Son of Man"],"."],["div",{"id":"38c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.38c","order":"03.04.008.4805"},["b","38c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-mark/8.42-43"},["span.small","JST"],"Mark 8:42–43 (Appendix)"],"."]]}
